  m_Name: ScenarioData-6
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ScenarioText: 'The Reveal

    Years pass, and the workplace begins to feel less
    like a company and more like an autonomous dictatorship. Every decision is made
    by AI, and human authority seems to be disappearing. Your daily assignments become
    increasingly suspicious, most of your work now involves collecting personal data
    related to politics, academics, and entertainment, while genuinely dangerous
    content is rarely intercepted.


    Unable to ignore your doubts any longer,
    you decide that today you will confront Boss Jackson and demand an explanation.
    You believe he still has the authority to answer your questions. Instead, you
    are about to uncover the truth behind the company you returned to.'
  CompanyHeirarchySprites: []
